
                        Section 2 - Notes
                         LABEL Instruction

1.  Dockerfile in this directory.

    $ cat Dockerfile
    # Dockerfile for LABEL instruction
    FROM busybox
    LABEL maintainer="Joe Jones <joe@company.com>"
    LABEL version="1.0"

2.  Build image.

    $ docker build -t label . 

3.  Inspect image for labels.

    $ docker inspect label | grep maintainer 
        "maintainer": "Joe Jones <joe@company.com>",
        "maintainer": "Joe Jones <joe@company.com>",

    $ docker inspect label | grep version 
        "LABEL version=1.0"
        "version": "1.0"
        "version": "1.0"

